  <exercise id="fs-idp96060096">
    <problem id="fs-idm44087488">
      <para id="fs-idm16836992">Which of the following was <emphasis effect="italics">not</emphasis> an outcome of the Underwood Tariff Act?</para>
		<list id="fs-idm12982144" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha"><item>It reduced tariffs 15 percent across all imports.</item>
				<item>It eliminated tariffs for steel.</item>
				<item>It eliminated tariffs for iron ore.</item>
				<item>It established a federal banking system to oversee tariffs.</item>
			</list>
    </problem>
